videos.headline: Florida defense comes up big with two blocks

videos.description: Kasey Hill with the ball, he drives and splits defenders for the bucket and the and-1.
videos.headline: Hill splits the Duke defense for the and-1
Amile Jefferson uses a strong move to make a lay-up in traffic

videos.description: 1H (5:37) DUKE Amile Jefferson made Dunk. Assisted by Grayson Allen.
videos.headline: Amile Jefferson slams down the two-handed jam

videos.description: KeVaughn Allen tries to score for Florida, but Amile Jefferson blocks the shot.
videos.headline: Amile Jefferson protects the rim with a solid block

videos.description: Jayson Tatum gets the ball from Luke Kennard and manages to score a layup before the buzzer to give Duke a 41-31 lead over Florida at the half.
videos.headline: Tatum's lay-in beats the buzzer and pads Duke's lead

videos.description: Florida Head Coach Mike White discusses how good Duke is
videos.headline: Florida Head Coach Mike White discusses how good Duke is

videos.description: Off a Duke miss, Florida takes the ball the other way. John Egbunu gets it and goes in for the dunk.
videos.headline: John Egbunu throws down a dunk in transition

videos.description: Grayson Allen misses the shot, but Amile Jefferson is there to put it back for Duke. It's not all good for Jefferson though as he loses his contact lens on the play.
videos.headline: Amile Jefferson loses contact lens on made lay-in

videos.description: 2H (14:33) DUKE Luke Kennard made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Grayson Allen.
videos.headline: Luke Kennard's 3-Pointer gives Duke their largest lead of the game

videos.description: 2H (12:34) DUKE Luke Kennard made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Grayson Allen.
videos.headline: Luke Kennard continues his great shooting night with another 3-Pointer

videos.description: 2H (10:52) DUKE Luke Kennard made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Amile Jefferson.
videos.headline: Luke Kennard continues hot night with another 3-pointer

videos.description: Off a Florida miss, Duke gets the ball back and passes to Jayson Tatum, who finishes with the layup.
videos.headline: Jayson Tatum makes easy layup off great Grayson Allen outlet pass
John Egbunu gets rejected by the rim, but draws the foul

videos.description: 2H (2:31) FLA Justin Leon made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Kasey Hill.
videos.headline: Justin Leon's 3-Pointer cuts the Duke lead to single digits
Luke Kennard makes lay-in in transition

videos.description: Amile Jefferson, Luke Kennard and Jayson Tatum combine to score 75 of Duke's 84 points in a victory over Florida.
videos.headline: Duke tops Florida to improve to 9-1
